 <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Rice </PERSON> has been correspondent for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Amman </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Jordan </LOCATION>, for three years and regularly covers other <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Eastern </LOCATION> countries.
